data.description: This rare property offers a custom built raised ranch home on 3.7 acres. Only 2.5mile from Crystal Lake. Onsite are two large steel pole barns and a full two bay heated and insulated garage with attached work rooms. The home is a single story berm style home with a mostly finished walkout basement. The open concept main floor leads to a wonderfully sized kitchen with a full island. The living room overlooks the large open yard and surrounding fields. The primary bedroom has a full attached bath with a walk-in closet. The lower walkout has bedrooms, a kitchenette, a small living room, and a full bath. It's practically a second house! A little polishing and finishing will make this a truly excellent find!
